The paper deals with visual understanding and reasoning, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed knowledge base framework involves incorporating textual and structured data, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The scalability aspect of the system involves optimization and learning, which are also key topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
